title: U2 - Live in New York - 1981-11-22 - Video
description:
U2
22 November 1981
New York, The Ritz 

Awesome concert from 1981! Video is pretty shitty by today's standards (4), but the audio is a 10! Professionally shot on VHS from the back of the hall. Regardless, it's a must see for any true U2 fan! It's funny seeing the band jump around, so much energy in youth. Oh, and Fuck You, Henry Rollins.



Video: NTSC, 720X480, 4:3, 29,97 fps, 8994 kbps
Audio: ac3, 448 kbps

Remixed by ONE8UNG
